</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">SDS</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="M140690-B27" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Purpose</ph></title><p class="- topic/p ">Through the SDS interface, you can start various SDS tests on the system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> A training video is available in the training video section: See 
<xref href="http://localhost:20346/VIDEO00394EN.US/video13/index.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>Introduction to the Colorado SDS</xref> 
