</p></li><li id="LI_1AF75BE527DC4BE8BAFD0482006A9280" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Tap the service button on the printer operator panel. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7B6C9515-D511-499E-A971-5DA90B93D427" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-92F000EA-B153-4541-9AFA-BA04B1A7C1AE-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-92F000EA-B153-4541-9AFA-BA04B1A7C1AE-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Adam will start. 
</p><fig id="GUID-909DE7ED-ECFF-4D72-B3CA-86DD13DEC877" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B6668541-64AB-4653-830A-F31F115D8B85-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B6668541-64AB-4653-830A-F31F115D8B85-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">As soon as Adam is ready tap the SDS button. 
</p><fig id="GUID-32D5E12B-EADF-43CB-9E5A-A8199A4C353D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F0540FA2-3FAD-4386-A289-4FBAEFCBB336-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F0540FA2-3FAD-4386-A289-4FBAEFCBB336-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">You are in the SDS now. 
